@Deleted User Personally I think messages that have been answered should be left alone so you can see the whole thread, it just smacks of censorship deleting stuff and makes it too hard to follow the conversations...
maybe move any chat not relevant to a question here or if you must remove questions from FR so we don't lose stuff...  It might not appear important or useful to you but it might be to someone else...
Also, dunno if it's possible but maybe make it so that only the SA folks and mods can post gifs to the FR

@Gawain Replying to ⁠archived-foundation-room⁠ : I agree, that could work very well. But it is paramount the community first understands there will only be 2 ships to start with.

If they expect more (and I am afraid this is the case), then we could get a big wave of negativity rolling over the project.

So we'll have to make sure to get this info out there
